info.author: Ignacio Alvarez
info.description: A short Django app that adds a button in the Djangouser admin page. When a superuser clicks the button, they are instantly logged in as that user.
info.name: django-impersonation
info.summary: An app to add a 'Log in as this user' button in the Djangouser admin page.
